com.percussion.integration
Class PSColumn

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.integration.PSColumn

public class PSColumn
extends Object

This class holds the information used to create the return HTML data from a PSSearch object. It is just a way of indicating what label a user would want to show as the column header for the specified field,

See Also:
for more information.
